content: As an AI language model, I don't have personal experiences but in general, women may begin to see some effects of testosterone therapy within 3-6 months, including increased muscle mass, improved energy levels and mood, and decreased body fat. However, full results may take up to 12 months to become apparent. It is important to note that individual response to testosterone therapy can vary, and it is essential to work closely with a healthcare provider to monitor health and adjust treatment as needed.
